Title: 121: Building a Successful Data Science Practice and How to be an Effective Data Scientist
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Senior Data Scientist at the Australian Federal Government, Dr. Alex Antic. You will hear how Alex loves meet-ups and how he spreads the word about data science, learn the 3 things you need to build a successful data practice, know the 4 point framework in becoming an effective data scientist, and listen to his incredible career journey, including investment banks, insurance & government.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/121
